sequenceDiagram
    participant AGENT as "arckit-datascout agent"
    participant API_CAT as "api.gov.uk<br/>(Data Standards Authority)"
    participant DASH as "api.gov.uk/dashboard"
    participant DEV_HUB as "Department Developer Hub<br/>(HMRC, NHS Digital, Defra)"
    participant DATA_GOV as "data.gov.uk<br/>(Open Data Portal)"
    participant OUTPUT as "research/ARC-{PID}-DSCT-{NUM}.md"
    
    Note over AGENT: Step 7: UK Government API Discovery
    AGENT->>API_CAT: WebFetch https://www.api.gov.uk/
    API_CAT-->>AGENT: Current catalogue of UK public sector APIs<br/>(JSON metadata: dept, status, docs URL)
    
    AGENT->>DASH: WebFetch https://www.api.gov.uk/dashboard/
    DASH-->>AGENT: Department API counts + contact info
    
    AGENT->>API_CAT: WebSearch "site:api.gov.uk [category]"<br/>(e.g., "site:api.gov.uk geospatial")
    API_CAT-->>AGENT: Filtered APIs by category
    
    Note over AGENT: Step 7.1: Department Developer Hubs
    AGENT->>DEV_HUB: WebSearch "[Department] developer hub API"<br/>(e.g., "HMRC developer hub API")
    DEV_HUB-->>AGENT: Hub URL (e.g., developer.service.hmrc.gov.uk)
    
    AGENT->>DEV_HUB: WebFetch [Hub URL]
    DEV_HUB-->>AGENT: Production APIs, auth methods<br/>(OAuth2, API keys), rate limits,<br/>sandbox environments, onboarding docs
    
    Note over AGENT: Step 7.2: Bulk Datasets
    AGENT->>DATA_GOV: WebFetch https://www.data.gov.uk/
    DATA_GOV-->>AGENT: Datasets index (CSV, JSON, SPARQL endpoints)
    
    AGENT->>DATA_GOV: WebSearch "site:data.gov.uk [category]"<br/>(e.g., "site:data.gov.uk transport")
    DATA_GOV-->>AGENT: Relevant datasets with download links
    
    Note over AGENT: Extract per-source metadata
    AGENT->>OUTPUT: Evaluation Cards per source:<br/>- Provider, License (OGL/CC/proprietary)<br/>- Format (REST/GraphQL/CSV/SPARQL)<br/>- Auth, Rate Limits, Update Frequency<br/>- Geographic/Temporal Coverage<br/>- Quality Indicators, Documentation Links
